    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You bestow luck upon your allies. All allies within range gain a +1 luck bonus to attack rolls, skill checks, ability checks, and saving throws. This bonus lasts as long as you concentrate. You may spend a spell point as a free action to allow this effect to continue for 1 round per caster level without concentration.</p>\n<h2 id=\"toc2\"><span>Word</span></h2>\n<p>As a standard action, you may invoke a word of power, affecting a single creature or object within close range. Words are subject to spell resistance.</p>\n<p>When you gain the Fate sphere, you gain the following word:</p>\n",
